videos.description: Auburn's Allen Flanigan blocks Darius Brown II on the layup attempt, which leads to J'Von McCormick setting up Anfernee McLemore for an alley-oop jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Flanigan's block leads to McLemore alley-oop) 2019/11/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Flanigan's block leads to McLemore alley-oop

videos.description: Tyrell Jones gets the rebound after Anfernee McLemore blocks Jared Pearre, then passes to Devan Cambridge on the break for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McLemore's block sets up Cambridge's fast break slam) 2019/11/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: McLemore's block sets up Cambridge's fast break slam

videos.description: J'Von McCormick gets the steal and throws a lob to Danjel Purifoy for the easy fast-break dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McCormick steal leads to easy alley-oop slam for Purifoy) 2019/11/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCormick steal leads to easy alley-oop slam for Purifoy

videos.description: Danjel Purifoy elevates to drop the hammer on an emphatic dunk to cap the fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Purifoy drops the hammer on the fast break) 2019/11/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purifoy drops the hammer on the fast break

videos.description: J'Von McCormick goes behind his back to lose his defender then throws a sweet lob pass to Anfernee McLemore for a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McCormick crosses defender and throws sweet lob to McLemore) 2019/11/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCormick crosses defender and throws sweet lob to McLemore

videos.description: J'Von McCormick knifes through the defense and tosses up a lob to Isaac Okoro for the emphatic slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McCormick racks up 14th assist with lob to Okoro) 2019/11/15 ESHEET
